```
LEFT JOIN chi_attribute_values as cav ON cav.id = cpnav.attribute_value_id
GROUP BY cpnav.product_id, cav.attribute_product_id
HAVING COUNT(cav.attribute_product_id) > 1 AND cav.attribute_product_id = 233;
```
